<html>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #F2E5BF;
            min-width: 1000px;
            width: auto !important;
            width: 1000px;
        }
        .cute_content {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: auto;
            background: none;
            border: 2px dotted #000;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .cute_content #logo{
            width: 23%;
            display: block;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .cute_content #cute_nav {
            background-color: #BFCBF1;
            border: 2px dotted #000;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #000;
            margin: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .cute_content #cute_nav a {
            float: left;
            color: #000;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;            
        }
        .cute_content #cute_nav a:hover {
            background-color: #f1c0cc;      
        }
        .cute_content #cute_nav a.active {
            background-color: #84ccdc;
            text-decoration: underline;      
        }
        .cute_content #cute_nav #cute_nav_c a{
            float: none;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%); 
        }
        .cute_content #cute_nav #cute_nav_r {
            float: right;
        }
        .cute_content #video_con{
            display: inherit;
            border: 2px solid;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #000;
        }
        .cute_content #sch_con{
            background-color: #BFCBF1;
            display: inherit;
            text-align: center;
            color: #000;
            margin-top: 10px;
            table-layout: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            border: 2px dotted #000;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #000;
        }
        .cute_content #sch_title {
            background-color: #f1c0cc;
            margin: auto;
            margin-top: 10px;
            width: max-content;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 2px dotted #000;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #000;
        }
        .cute_content #sch_con th, td{
            width: 200px;
        }
        
        .cute_content #vj_info {
            margin-top: 15px;
            display: flex;
        }
        .cute_content #c_vj_avi {
            height: 270px;
            border: 2px solid #000;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #000;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .cute_content #vj_name{
            background-color: #BFCBF1;
            width: max-content;
            text-align: center;
            display: inherit;
            margin: 10% 10px 0px 10px;
            border: 2px dotted #000;
            height: min-content;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #000;
        }
         .cute_content #vj_name h2{
            margin: 0;
        }
         .cute_content #vj_name th, td{
            width: 200px;
        }
         .cute_content #site_news{
            width: 50%;
            overflow-y: scroll;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            border: 2px dotted #000;
            margin-left: 10px;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #000;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cute_content #site_news #n_post_con{
            width: 100%;
            display: inline;
        }
         .cute_content #site_news #n_post_con .n_post{
            margin: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            width: 400px;
            display: block;
            border: 2px dotted;
            box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px #000;
        }
        .cute_content #site_news #n_post_con .n_post td{
            width: 100%
         }
         
         @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .cute_content #cute_nav a, .cute_content #cute_nav #cute_nav_r {
                float: none;
                display: block;
            }           

            .cute_content #cute_nav #cute_nav_c a {
                position: relative;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                transform: none;
            }
        }
    </style>
    <head>
        <title>/a/cute.tv</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        
    <div class="cute_content">
        <img id="logo" src="l.png">
        <div id="cute_nav">
            <div id="cute_nav_c">
                <a class="active" href="/">Stream</a>
            </div>
                <a href="/staff">Staff</a>
                <a href="/about">About</a>
            <div id="cute_nav_r">
                <a href="https://github.com/applesaucyy/acutetv" target="_blank">Repo</a>
                <a href="">Sign In</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h2>Welcome to a-cute.tv. A 24/7 video station to watch cute and dumb stuff. Mainly anime. This site is new and i'm not really a web-dev kind of person, so bear with me if the site fucks up. Uh, source repo is <a href="https://github.com/applesaucyy/acutetv">here</a>. Ok, thats all. More updates coming soon!</h2>
    </div>
    
    </body>
</html>

